snippet.title: Plead with the Mountain God - Trailer
snippet.description:
Download the game for free at http://potentially-odd.itch.io/plead-with-the-mountain-god

Plead with the Mountain God is a somber dark fantasy/horror-themed platformer made for the Haunted PS1 Summer of Screams Jam.

Survive the perilous climb and plead with the mountain god to resurrect your beloved.

Join our Discord:
https://discord.gg/8acMKGcRU4

Follow Potentially Odd:
